Maintainer: Jack Baker <j.baker1@lancaster.ac.uk>
Description: R library for performing stochastic gradient MCMC
  including SGLD, SGHMC, SGNHT and control variate methods. Library is built on 'TensorFlow'
  <https://www.tensorflow.org/>, a library for efficient numerical computation.
